# ─── Launcher backend runtime uploads ──────────────────────────────
# v1.9 — Admin-uploaded APKs land in data/apks/ (can be 50–200 MB
# per file → blows past GitHub's 100 MB hard limit), and their
# auto-extracted icons land in data/apk_icons/.  data/tile_apks/
# holds APKs attached to dock tiles (also user uploads, also can
# be tens of MB).  None of these directories should be tracked:
# they're per-installation runtime state, NOT source code.  The
# store.json index next to them IS tracked (it's tiny metadata
# describing what's in those folders).
launcher-backend/data/apks/*
launcher-backend/data/apk_icons/*
launcher-backend/data/tile_apks/*
!launcher-backend/data/apks/.gitkeep
!launcher-backend/data/apk_icons/.gitkeep
!launcher-backend/data/tile_apks/.gitkeep
